snippet: Dominic Thiem, an Austrian qualifier, scored the biggest victory of his young career when he rallied for a 1-6, 6-2, 6-4 win over third-ranked Stanislas Wawrinka at the Madrid Open.
abstract: Australian qualifier Dominic Thiem beats third-ranked Stanislas Wawrinka at the Madrid Open.
lead_paragraph: Dominic Thiem, an Austrian qualifier, scored the biggest victory of his young career when he rallied for a 1-6, 6-2, 6-4 win over third-ranked Stanislas Wawrinka at the Madrid Open.
